[src:gson-json-java/reflection-computer-programming] It contains one method, `static Class<?> getCallerClass(int depth)` for obtaining the class making a call at a specified depth.
[src:gson-json-java/reflection-computer-programming] This is now superseded by using the class `java.lang.StackWalker.StackFrame` and its method `Class<?> getDeclaringClass()` .
